metadata.name: Garden of Imagination #40
metadata.description:
The more a garden can sharpen all senses, the better.

The garden is one of the most artistic expressions where the five human senses are explored (sight, smell, sound, taste and touch).
It's very good to be impressed by many different colors and shapes, feel the perfume of flowers, feel the textures of plants, taste the fruits and hear the noise of leaves and birds. The more a garden manages to sharpen all the senses, the better it fulfills its role.
The challenge of this project is to provide as many sensations as possible, some you will get visually and others you will need imagination. Imagination is an essential part of this project. There are different species from different cultures that, after becoming relatives, start to interact with each other.

The Garden of Imagination is layered artwork generated from a pool of previously rendered digital assets developed for several months.

- Use the "S" key to export an image.

metadata.name: Miniscapes #30
metadata.description:
Miniscapes merges generative code (Rich's bit) with meticulously designed scenes and elements (Rick's bit), to create minimalist landscapes intended to charm, delight, and surprise.

Our aim was to convey as much as possible with as little as possible by using simple shapes and lines to represent a wide variety of natural landscapes.

We hope that you find as much joy in owning a Miniscape as we did in creating them.

Controls (in live view):
- Press [s] to save the current image
- Press [p] to pause an animated output
- Press [r] to reset an animated output (this will also pause)

metadata.name: Purgatory #19
metadata.description:
Purgatory is a place where the souls of those who have died in a state of grace are purified from venial sins or from the temporal punishment which still remains to be endured. As such, it is seen as a temporary and final purification that brings about the achievement of the holiness necessary to enter the joy of heaven.

Click to fly around and explore your personal purgatory.

metadata.name: NEBULAE #62
metadata.description:
NEBULAE invites you to deep space exploration to search for rare nebulas. As a space explorer you will most likely encounter an NGC, the common nebula type, but on your travels there is an possibility you will witness the powerful creative forces of the universe.. or discover something even more magical.

This project was created with randomly generated Embergen particle simulations combined with cables.gl background setup. I want to deeply thank Murat Atimtay for all the help with this first generative mint and VerticalCryptoArt & somaticbits for their helpful resources.


[e] save as png

I hope this series sparks your imagination and love for color as it did for me.

- Walt

metadata.name: Morixels Mans #777
metadata.description:
The Morixels Mans is unique Random Generated 10,000 PFP NFTs, and this collection is for people like me who are nostalgic for pixel arts.
This collection is manually designed.
The original Artwork was designed in 24 by 24 pixels and then resized to 1080 by 1080 resolution. 
The number of Traits in this collection is 12 (120 layers) and it has the ability to make 31,091,558,400 NFTs.
Some â€‹layers are less than 1 percent of the total, some 100 percent, and some between 0.1 and 100 percent.
To create balance, these NFTs are randomly minted, and this is a chance for everyone to get a rare version. So due to the low price of these NFTs, if the rare version did not belong to you, it is still possible for you to mint the new NFTs.
To Produce this collection, all the layers were designed pixel by pixel, which was time-consuming and difficult. And this greatly increases the value of this collection.

Because this is an NFT in PFP format, you can put it on your avatar on Twitter or Instagram.

Twitter: @Morixels

Website: https://morixels.com/

Designed by: @morteza_yousefy
Made in 2022
